5+...

527
00:59:11,714 --> 00:59:15,047
- Shall l recite a poetry foryou?
- No need! l'm studying!

528
00:59:16,185 --> 00:59:18,085
l said, l'm studying!

529
00:59:18,254 --> 00:59:21,587
''Who created
the sparrows that fly?''

530
00:59:22,458 --> 00:59:24,688
-All right, l'll go.
- l'll beat you!

531
00:59:27,196 --> 00:59:29,096
Brother Rahul.

532
00:59:30,199 --> 00:59:32,360
Shall l recite a poetry foryou?

533
00:59:33,202 --> 00:59:34,601
Yes, please.

534
00:59:38,441 --> 00:59:43,640
''Who created
the sparrows that fly?''

535
00:59:45,748 --> 00:59:50,685
''Who created you and me?''

536
00:59:53,289 --> 00:59:56,690
''The Lord is present in everything''

537
01:00:01,297 --> 01:00:03,197
Whose picture is this?

538
01:00:03,366 --> 01:00:04,765
My papa's.

539
01:00:05,501 --> 01:00:07,196
ls this how your papa looks?

540
01:00:07,370 --> 01:00:10,203
l don't know.
Perhaps this is how he looks.

541
01:00:10,373 --> 01:00:11,806
Where's he?

542
01:00:16,346 --> 01:00:17,745
He must be dead.

543
01:00:17,914 --> 01:00:21,748
No! Mummy used to say that
he has gone very far away.

544
01:00:21,951 --> 01:00:23,851
And that he'd
surely return someday.

545
01:00:24,020 --> 01:00:29,788
l'd seen another child's father
go somewhere far away, on TV.

546
01:00:29,959 --> 01:00:32,792
His mummy too had said that
his father would return.

547
01:00:32,962 --> 01:00:35,897
But he was dead.
And the boy didn't even know!

548
01:00:36,399 --> 01:00:38,299
Films are not reality.

549
01:00:38,901 --> 01:00:41,301
Yes, indeed. They are films.

550
01:00:41,471 --> 01:00:44,099
l'll tell papa.
He'll find yourfather.

551
01:00:44,440 --> 01:00:45,839
How will he find him?

552
01:00:48,444 --> 01:00:51,811
My papa is very clever.
Watch, he will find yourfather!

553
01:00:51,981 --> 01:00:53,915
Mini! ...What are you doing here?

554
01:00:54,450 --> 01:00:56,384
Playing with Brother Rahul.

555
01:00:56,552 --> 01:00:57,951
Go and sleep.

556
01:01:01,357 --> 01:01:03,257
Since when did Rahul
become your brother?!

557
01:01:09,365 --> 01:01:11,265
What's that you're swallowing?

558
01:01:11,434 --> 01:01:12,765
Sleeping pills.

559
01:01:16,906 --> 01:01:19,306
Will taking sleeping pills
solve anything?

560
01:01:23,413 --> 01:01:25,813
How often have
l apologised to you!

561
01:01:27,417 --> 01:01:30,352
